target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3614536\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mdg1665702628370.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mdg1665702628370.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mdg1665702628370.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mdg1665702628370\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Label Font (\n                              LabelFont)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Font for the label associated with this widget. The specified label font is also used in widgets that support tool tip text. If not specified, the font definition in the application's <span class=\"ph filepath\">.ini</span> file is used.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__topic_d105170e1_d105171e1_d105172e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__p_d105173e1_d105174e1_d105175e1\">LabelFont<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">FontName</var></p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__p_d105176e1_d105177e1_d105178e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">$properties(FLD1)=\n               \"labelfont=HyperLabel\"</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__table_d12425e1_d12426e1_d12427e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__table_d12425e1_d12426e1_d12427e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__table_d12425e1_d12426e1_d12427e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mdg1665702628370__table_d12425e1_d12426e1_d12427e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FontName</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mdg1665702628370__table_d12425e1_d12426e1_d12427e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Name of a logical font, as defined in the [screen] section of\n                              <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__section_w652ab1b5b3_w653ab1b5_w654ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d704142e124\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__table_d12428e1_d12429e1_d12430e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dynamic?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported in Grid?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dependencies:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__section_w655ab1b5b5_w656ab1b5_w657ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d704142e188\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__p_d105185e1_d105186e1_d105187e1\">If the selected font is larger than the available\n            space in the label, the label can behave unpredictably at run time. To correct this,\n            choose a smaller font or enlarge the size of the label.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__section_rdh_tst_ywb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d704142e197\">Grid Widget</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__p_d105191e1_d105192e1_d105193e1\">For grid widgets, this property specifies the font\n            for field labels (headings). It overrides the value set for individual fields.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__section_yn1_5st_ywb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d704142e206\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__ul_l35_vst_ywb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41900e1_d41901e1_d41902e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fxi1688449052174.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fxi1688449052174.html\" title=\"The ucheckbox widget enables the user to set a Boolean value in a form component. Uniface provides a logical widget called CheckBox, which is mapped to ucheckbox.\">ucheckbox (CheckBox)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41903e1_d41904e1_d41905e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zfr1695290811319.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zfr1695290811319.html\" title=\"Start the Microsoft Windows Color dialog box.\">colorbox</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41906e1_d41907e1_d41908e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gzs1665702629046.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gzs1665702629046.html\" title=\"The (ucolorlist) widget displays a list of system or web colors for selection in a form component. Uniface provides a logical widget called ColorList, which is mapped to ucolorlist.\">ucolorlist (ColorList)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41909e1_d41910e1_d41911e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vmo1688449724415.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vmo1688449724415.html\" title=\"The ucombobox widget combines an input field with a drop-down list. It allows users to select one item from a previously defined list, or enter their own data instead. It is applicable only to form components. Uniface provides a logical widget called ComboBox, which is mapped to ucombobox.\">ucombobox (Combo Box)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41912e1_d41913e1_d41914e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrc1665702631553.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrc1665702631553.html\" title=\"The CommandButton is a logical widget that enables a user to initiate an action by clicking the button.\">CommandButton</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41915e1_d41916e1_d41917e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wrn1665702633674.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wrn1665702633674.html\" title=\"The DropTarget logical widget accepts input dragged from a DragSource, other Uniface application, or Microsoft Windows Explorer. The data that is transferred consists of a Uniface list.\">DropTarget</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41918e1_d41919e1_d41920e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fud1688450548955.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fud1688450548955.html\" title=\"The udropdownlist widget is a field-level widget that can display a list of valid options in a list below the input field, so that the user can select one. It is applicable only to form components.\">udropdownlist (DropDownList)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41921e1_d41922e1_d41923e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"klb1688454363706.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/klb1688454363706.html\" title=\"Default logical widget for entering and displaying data in a field in a Form or Report.\">EditBox</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41924e1_d41925e1_d41926e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"clg1695282025414.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/clg1695282025414.html\" title=\"The egrid widget displays data in a tabular format, in which the rows are occurrences of an entity and the columns are fields. It is an entity-level widget that is only applicable to form components.\">egrid (Grid)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41927e1_d41928e1_d41929e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ied1665702642247.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ied1665702642247.html\" title=\"The uhtml widget is a field-level widget in a form component that renders HTML code (including HTML, CSS, and JavaScript) or displays a web page (when the field value is a URL prefixed by an ampersand (&amp;www.mysite.com/doc/index.html). Uniface provides a logical widget called HTML, which is mapped to uhtml.\">uhtml (HTML Widget)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41930e1_d41931e1_d41932e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dzy1665702618507.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dzy1665702618507.html\" title=\"This property determines whether the widget behaves as a hyperlink (True; default) or a dynamic label False.\">Hyperlink</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41933e1_d41934e1_d41935e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rez1688451198680.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rez1688451198680.html\" title=\"The ulistbox widget is a field-level widget that displays an open list in which one or more values can be selected. It can only be used in form components.\">ulistbox (ListBox )</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41936e1_d41937e1_d41938e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gls1665702643795.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gls1665702643795.html\" title=\"The umap widget defines areas on an image that allow the user to interact by clicking on that area. It can only be used in form components. Uniface provides a logical widget called Map, which is mapped to umap.\">umap (Map)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41939e1_d41940e1_d41941e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bwv1665702644903.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bwv1665702644903.html\" title=\"The umeter widget displays the value of a Numeric field on a gauge for which there is a predefined range of values marked around the outer edge. Uniface provides a logical widget called Meter, which is mapped to umeter.\">umeter (Meter)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41942e1_d41943e1_d41944e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"svk1665702646925.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/svk1665702646925.html\" title=\"The umonthcalendar widget displays a month calendar to enable the user to select a date. Uniface provides a logical widget called MonthCalendar, which is mapped to umonthcalendar.\">(umonthcalendar) MonthCalendar</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41945e1_d41946e1_d41947e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rdo1665702649920.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rdo1665702649920.html\" title=\"The uOleContainer widget displays an embedded OLE object, enabling you to define links to OLE objects in Uniface applications.\">uOleContainer (OleContainer)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41948e1_d41949e1_d41950e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ddd1665702643397.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ddd1665702643397.html\" title=\"The uoutputbox widget displays streaming text data. The data may come from a specified Output Channel, or be explicitly added. By default, it does not listen to any channel. Uniface provides a logical widget called OutputBox, which is mapped to uoutputbox.\">uoutputbox (OutputBox)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41951e1_d41952e1_d41953e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rgn1665702634165.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rgn1665702634165.html\" title=\"Image to use as the background image on the map widget.\">Image Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41954e1_d41955e1_d41956e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yye1665702650577.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yye1665702650577.html\" title=\"The uradiogroup widget displays a set of mutually exclusive choices as a group of radio buttons. Uniface provides a logical widget called RadioGroup, which is mapped to uradiogroup.\">uradiogroup (RadioGroup)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41957e1_d41958e1_d41959e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qwk1688451210612.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qwk1688451210612.html\" title=\"The urtfeditbox widget is used to display and edit text as Rich Text Format (RTF), which supports formatting such as font and color attributes, text alignment, indentation, and lists. Uniface provides a logical widget called RichEditBox, which is mapped to urtfeditbox.\">urtfeditbox (RichEditBox)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41960e1_d41961e1_d41962e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"foe1665702651174.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/foe1665702651174.html\" title=\"The uslider widget allows users to edit a numeric value in a field by sliding an indicator in a set of a previously defined range of values. Uniface provides a logical widget called Slider, which is mapped to uslider.\">uslider (Slider)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41963e1_d41964e1_d41965e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lxs1665702651483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lxs1665702651483.html\" title=\"The uspinbutton widget enables the user to enter or select a numeric value by clicking a button to increase or decrease a value by a predefined interval within a predefined range. Uniface provides a logical widget called SpinButton, which is mapped to uspinbutton.\">uspinbutton (SpinButton)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41966e1_d41967e1_d41968e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bzj1665702641924.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bzj1665702641924.html\" title=\"The utab widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tab, which is mapped to utab.\">utab (Tab)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41969e1_d41970e1_d41971e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gyf1688451219719.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gyf1688451219719.html\" title=\"The utabex widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. The utabex widget is highly customizable, allowing extensive control over the appearance and behavior of the tabs. Uniface provides a logical widget called TabEx, which is mapped to utabex.\">utabex (TabEx)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdg1665702628370__li_d41972e1_d41973e1_d41974e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gge1665702634237.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gge1665702634237.html\" title=\"The utree widget enables users to view and navigate structured data as a hierarchy. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tree, which is mapped to utree.\">utree (Tree)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614536\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614536\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Label Font ( LabelFont) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Label Font ( LabelFont) Font for the label associated with this widget. The specified label font is also used in widgets that support tool tip text. If not specified, the font definition in the application's .ini file is used. LabelFont = FontName Example: $properties(FLD1)= \"labelfont=HyperLabel\" Value Description FontName Name of a logical font, as defined in the [screen] section of usys.ini . Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: None Description If the selected font is larger than the available space in the label, the label can behave unpredictably at run time. To correct this, choose a smaller font or enlarge the size of the label. Grid Widget For grid widgets, this property specifies the font for field labels (headings). It overrides the value set for individual fields. Applies To ucheckbox (CheckBox) colorbox ucolorlist (ColorList) ucombobox (Combo Box) CommandButton DropTarget udropdownlist (DropDownList) EditBox egrid (Grid) uhtml (HTML Widget) Hyperlink ulistbox (ListBox ) umap (Map) umeter (Meter) (umonthcalendar) MonthCalendar uOleContainer (OleContainer) uoutputbox (OutputBox) Image Name uradiogroup (RadioGroup) urtfeditbox (RichEditBox) uslider (Slider) uspinbutton (SpinButton) utab (Tab) utabex (TabEx) utree (Tree) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}